Howard L. MILLSAP et al. v. UNITED STATES of America. No. 7353. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. May 16, 1963. G. L. Spence, Riverton, Wyo., for appellants. Robert N. Chaffin, U. S. Atty., Cheyenne, Wyo., for appellee.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Docketed and dismissed May 16, 1963, on motion of appellee, for failure to prosecute. 208 F.Supp. 511.
